Data integration is quite messy
It has become more difficult as things have started to become complex

Integration Complexity
-> No system of record
-> Synchronization is hard
-> Scaling ETL is hard
-> Processing is error-prone

First thing that we do for integration architecture is to use events instead of tables (as source of truth)

We need to be able to go back in time. For this a ledger like system must be present